(125, 'Step 1', '<p><span><br class="kix-line-break" />All Mumineen doing Niyyat to travel to Al Moizziya tul Qahera for the Ziyarat of Raas Al Imam Al Husain (AS), Mashaahid of Ahle Bait (AS) and Jawamea Fatemiyah, should read and abide by the following instructions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>1. To travel to Al Moizziya tul Qahera, please log on to the Faiz-e-Haakimi website:&nbsp;</span><a href="http://www.faizehaakimi.com/"><span>www.faizehaakimi.com</span></a><span>which will help you to organize your trip.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>2. All Zuwwar Kiraam who are not traveling through a Tour Operator, are required to fill out our online form (even if in Transit), provided on our website&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;well before their arrival. If you make any changes in your Itinerary after initially informing us, please e-mail us the changes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>3. All Zuwwar Kiraam will need a valid Waraqat ut Tarkhis and their E-jamaat card.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>4. If you have any problems obtaining a visa please email us and we will try and assist you. Nationals of the US, UK, Canada, Western Europe, France, etc. among other nations may be eligible for an "</span><span>on arrival</span><span>" visas. Please inquire with your travel agent, local Egyptian diplomatic mission, and airline before planning your trip. The "<strong>on arrival</strong>" visa will cost&nbsp;<strong>15$</strong>&nbsp;per person.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>5. Before coming to Al Moizziya-tul-Qahera you must have a confirmed return booking.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>6. All aged, disabled, patients, and anyone who requires assistance should give us prior information as to do our utmost to provide the required facilities (subject to availability).</span></p>\r\n<p><span>7. Muminaat should wear a Rida at all times and Mumineen should wear Libaas e Anwar (Kurta saya) while performing Ziyarat and attending Majaalis.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>8. Mumineen will follow the itinerary provided by us which will depend on the date of arrival and departure.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>9. Lawazim:</span></p>\r\n<table cellspacing="3" cellpadding="6" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style28" bgcolor="#999966" width="50%"><span><strong>Package</strong></span></td>\r\n<td class="style28" bgcolor="#808055"><span><strong>Adult&nbsp;<br />12 years and above<br />(as per passport)</strong></span></td>\r\n<td class="style28" bgcolor="#6f6f4a"><strong><span>Child&nbsp;<br />2-12 years<br />(as per passport)</span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">4 Nights<span class="style1">&nbsp;&raquo;&nbsp;<span><span class="style36">5th Day Dept</span></span></span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">320$&nbsp;<br />per Adult</td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">200$&nbsp;<br />per child</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">\r\n<p>Extra Nights &nbsp;5<sup>th&nbsp;</sup>-&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;9</span><sup>th</sup><span>&nbsp;night</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">\r\n<p><span>50$ per Night per Adult</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">\r\n<p><span>25$ per Night per Child</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">Transit<span class="style1">&nbsp;&raquo;<span class="style36">&nbsp;<span>Max. 2 Nights</span></span></span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">85$&nbsp;<br />per Night&nbsp;<br />per adult</td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">55$<br />per Night<br />per child</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">Long-stay<span class="style1"><br /><span><span class="style41">( Min.10 Nights )</span></span></span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">450$<br />per Night<br />per adult<br /><span><span class="style39">Transport not Included</span></span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">\r\n<p>320$ for 10 Nights &nbsp;<br /><span>Then onwards $25 per Night<br />per Child</span></p>\r\n<p><span><span class="style39">Transport not Included</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">Long-stay<span class="style1"><br /><span><span class="style41">( Min. 10 nights )</span></span></span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">55$&nbsp;<br />per Night<br />per adult<br /><span><span class="style39">Transport Included</span></span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">\r\n<p>320$ for 10 Nights &nbsp;<br />Then onwards $25 per Night<br />per Child</p>\r\n<p><span class="style39">Transport Included</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">Tour Leader&nbsp;<span class="style1">&raquo;<span class="style36">&nbsp;<span>(4Nights &amp; 5th day departure)</span></span></span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">180$&nbsp;<br />per adult</td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f7f4e8">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">Daawat E Haadiyah Khidmat Guzaar<br />(Kothar Mubarak, Al Jamea tus Saifiyah, Ummal keram, MSB Muraqebeen, Attalim, Mazaaraat Muqaddasah, Atabaat Aaliyah, Sigatul Yemen)<br />Valid Letter from concern IDARA to be produced upon request.</td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">160$&nbsp;<br />Per adult<br /><span>(4Nights &amp;&nbsp;<br />5th day departure)</span></td>\r\n<td class="style19" bgcolor="#f0ead2">100$<br />per child&nbsp;<br /><span>(4Nights &amp;&nbsp;<br />5th day departure</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span>10. Note for Transit package: Transit package includes Ziyarat of Imam Husain (AS) and other Mashaahid of Ahle Bait (AS), time permitting.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>11. We will only accept US Dollars in cash.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>12. You must give correct flight details &amp; arrival date so that we can receive you at Cairo International Airport. Please note that your lawazim will start from the date mentioned in your registration form.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>13. Your four day stay will include the following:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span>a) Raas Al Imam Al Husain (AS).</span><br />b) Moulatuna Zainab (AS).<br />c)Moulatuna Ruqaiyyah (AS).<br />d) Moulatuna Nafisa (AS).<br />e) Moulana Mohammed bin Abibakr (RA).<br />f) Moulana Malik ul Ashtar (RA).<br />g) Syedi Muqaddas Yusuf BS Najmuddin (QR).<br />h) Jame Anwar.<br />i) Jame Azhar.<br />j) Jame Aqmar.<br />k) Jame Lulua.<br />l) Jame Juyushi, (subject to permission).<br />m) Jame Ateeq.<br />n) Jame Ibn e Tuloon. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span>14.Also places of sightseeing in Cairo like (pyramids, Egyptian museum, etc.)</span></p>', '2013-09-22 00:00:00', '2013-05-11 08:44:00', 0, 1, -6, '', '0', 0),
